('690cdbfb8aedb9b957654b44', '1d7cb8f71c23db3ac7787537fcd85bfdd18a6d6c12bb03106afe85a2837af3aa', 1, 4, 11, 1, 1, 7, '3', 2, 'over 1 year of experience in related work', 'Bachelor', 'report writing;Risk assessment;Safety Check;Incident Handling;Understanding of Occupational Safety Law', 'communication;training;responsible;proactive;coordination', 'Occupational Safety;HSE;Safety Engineer;Chemistry;Chemical Technology;Labor Protection;Risk Assessment;Safety Regulations;Training;Incident Handling;Safety Check;Report Writing;Occupational Safety Law', 'Nhân Viên An Toàn Lao Động', 'https://www.topcv.vn/viec-lam/nhan-vien-an-toan-lao-dong/1943040.html?ta_source=JobSearchList_LinkDetail&u_sr_id=s4XIHaYEXJOre7nsJhGavErS23YpAtvoiB1VpQO0_1762450373', 0, 0, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Social insurance;Health insurance for relatives;Health insurance;Periodic health check-ups;Annual travel;Seniority allowance;13th month salary;Performance bonus', '2025-11-06', '2026-01-31', 'Responsible for the overall occupational safety work of the Factory. Develop, draft, and issue regulations, procedures, and guidelines on hygiene - safety - labor protection in accordance with legal regulations. Monitor, supervise, and inspect compliance with internal regulations and labor safety regulations throughout the Factory; promptly detect and warn of unsafe acts. Record violations, propose handling measures, and coordinate implementation of handling according to Factory regulations. Assess and analyze hazards - risks that cause unsafety; propose preventive and corrective measures and improve working conditions. Develop plans and organize training/education on occupational safety for new employees and annual periodic training. Coordinate with specialized departments/units in hygiene, occupational safety, and participate in related assessment and inspection programs. Summarize, prepare periodic reports, and perform other tasks as assigned by management. Graduated from University in related fields: Occupational 