ities. Plan and execute initiatives to reach target customers through suitable media channels such as social media, email, television, etc. Assist in analyzing marketing data (campaign results, conversion rates, website traffic, etc.) to shape future marketing strategies. Take on independent tasks within the assigned marketing plan.', 'Proficient in English : IELTS 6.5+ Education : Bachelor\'s degree in Marketing or a related field, with at least 3 years of professional experience in marketing . Strong understanding of branding , marketing strategies , and a passion for the industry. Solid knowledge of traditional and digital marketing methods and tools . Creative thinking skills and the ability to work independently. Strong teamwork skills and excellent communication abilities . Attention to detail and effective time management skills', 'Salary : VND 16mil - VND 25mil depending on experience and skill set Modern and dynamic working environment . High career advancement opportunities . Full benefits package ( social insurance , holiday leaves , 13th month salary , bonuses , company trips , etc.) as per labor laws, along with additional attractive perks. Domestic and international travel opportunities .', 'https://cdn-new.topcv.vn/unsafe/80x/https://static.topcv.vn/company_logos/682300a343ca21747124387.png', 'https://cv.neu.edu.vn/job/6914c7a18aedb9b957655012', '<ul><li>Tầng 13, Tòa nhà ICON4, 243A Đê La Thành, phường Láng Thượng</li><li>Tòa nhà của Công ty Cổ phần Trung tâm Công nghệ Phần mềm, TP Thái Nguyên</li></ul>', 'marketing-coordinator-thu-nhap-tu-16-25-trieu'),
